<i>noun</i>: 촬영장 [촤령장], 촬영소 [촤령소], 작업실 [자겁씰], 원룸 [], 스튜디오 [], 방송실 [방ː송실], 단칸방 [단칸빵], 단칸 [단칸] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>촬영장 [촤령장]</dt><br>
<dd>studio; filming site</dd><br>
<dd>영화나 사진 등을 촬영하는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>The area for shooting and producing a film, photograph, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>촬영소 [촤령소]</dt><br>
<dd>studio</dd><br>
<dd>영화 등을 찍고 만드는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>The space for shooting and producing a film, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>작업실 [자겁씰]</dt><br>
<dd>workroom; studio</dd><br>
<dd>일을 하는 방.</dd><br>
<dd>A room where one does work.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>원룸 []</dt><br>
<dd>studio</dd><br>
<dd>방 하나가 침실, 거실, 부엌, 식당의 기능을 모두 하는 집.</dd><br>
<dd>A house in which one room functions as a bedroom, living room, and kitchen.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>스튜디오 []</dt><br>
<dd>1. studio</dd><br>
<dd>방송국에서 녹음하거나 방송하는 공간.</dd><br>
<dd>The space for recording or broadcasting something in a broadcasting station.</dd><br>
<dd>2. studio</dd><br>
<dd>사진을 찍거나 그림 작업을 하는 장소.</dd><br>
<dd>A professional space for taking a photo or painting a picture.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>방송실 [방ː송실]</dt><br>
<dd>studio; broadcasting booth</dd><br>
<dd>방송 장비를 갖추고 방송을 내보내는 방.</dd><br>
<dd>A room with broadcasting equipments that sends out broadcasts.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단칸방 [단칸빵]</dt><br>
<dd>studio</dd><br>
<dd>한 칸으로 된 방.</dd><br>
<dd>A room without a separate living room or kitchen.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단칸 [단칸]</dt><br>
<dd>studio; single room</dd><br>
<dd>한 칸.</dd><br>
<dd>One room.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>